show.title: My Call Boy Billionaire Daddy
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/YX5Zae
show.description: She had it all until her own family's betrayal plunged her into destitution, leaving her vulnerable to a night of profound misunderstanding with a man she believed was a call boy. Years later, her world is shaken again when that very man, now a formidable businessman, reappears, deliberately playing different roles to scrutinize her true nature. Is his re-entry a chance for healing, a cruel manipulation, or merely fate's twisted design? As secrets unravel and the lines between past and present blur, their lives become a perilous dance. Will they find solace and connection, or are they destined to be forever ensnared by the echoes of their devastating first encounter?
